How do I update this listing?




                                             Twin Securities is based out of New York. Twin Securities is a large advisory firm with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $859,714,337 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $579,997,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 87.48%. Twin Securities's largest holding is Altaba, Inc. with shares held of 3,069,589.  Twin Securities has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 47 13F filings in our database for Twin Securities. 
                                           






